<div class="container" style="margin-top: 120px; margin-bottom: 60px; max-width: 800px; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;">
    <h1 style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; font-size: 2.5rem; color: #1e1b4b; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 10px;">&#272;i&#7873;u Kho&#7843;n D&#7883;ch V&#7909;</h1>
    <p style="text-align: center; color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 40px; font-size: 1.1rem;">Th&#7887;a thu&#7853;n ph&#225;p l&#253; quy &#273;&#7883;nh quy&#7873;n h&#7841;n v&#224; tr&#225;ch nhi&#7879;m khi s&#7917; d&#7909;ng TourBuddy.</p>

    <div style="background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); padding: 30px; color: #475569; line-height: 1.7;">
        <h2 style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #4f46e5; border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0; font-size: 1.5rem;">1. Ch&#7845;p nh&#7853;n c&#225;c &#273;i&#7873;u kho&#7843;n</h2>
        <p>B&#7857;ng vi&#7879;c &#273;&#259;ng k&#253; t&#224;i kho&#7843;n ho&#7863;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng d&#7883;ch v&#7909; c&#7911;a TourBuddy, b&#7841;n &#273;&#7891;ng &#253; ch&#7883;u s&#7921; r&#224;ng bu&#7897;c b&#7903;i c&#225;c quy &#273;&#7883;nh &#273;i&#7873;u kho&#7843;n d&#7883;ch v&#7909; n&#224;y. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n kh&#244;ng &#273;&#7891;ng &#253;, vui l&#242;ng ng&#7915;ng s&#7917; d&#7909;ng h&#7879; th&#7889;ng ngay l&#7853;p t&#7913;c.</p>

        <h2 style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #4f46e5; border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 30px; font-size: 1.5rem;">2. Tr&#225;ch nhi&#7879;m c&#7911;a kh&#225;ch h&#224;ng</h2>
        <p>Ng&#432;&#7901;i d&#249;ng cam k&#7871;t cung c&#7845;p th&#244;ng tin c&#225; nh&#226;n v&#224; th&#244;ng tin h&#224;nh kh&#225;ch ch&#237;nh x&#225;c khi th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7863;t tour. B&#7841;n t&#7921; ch&#7883;u tr&#225;ch nhi&#7879;m v&#7873; t&#237;nh b&#7843;o m&#7853;t c&#7911;a t&#224;i kho&#7843;n c&#225; nh&#226;n v&#224; c&#225;c giao d&#7883;ch ph&#225;t sinh t&#7915; t&#224;i kho&#7843;n c&#7911;a m&#236;nh.</p>

        <h2 style="font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; color: #4f46e5; border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 30px; font-size: 1.5rem;">3. Thay &#273;&#7893;i &#273;i&#7873;u kho&#7843;n</h2>
        <p>Ch&#250;ng t&#244;i c&#243; quy&#7873;n c&#7853;p nh&#7853;t ho&#7863;c thay &#273;&#7893;i &#273;i&#7873;u kho&#7843;n d&#7883;ch v&#7909; v&#224;o b&#7845;t k&#7923; l&#250;c n&#224;o m&#224; kh&#244;ng c&#7847;n th&#244;ng b&#225;o tr&#432;&#7899;c. Phi&#234;n b&#7843;n &#273;i&#7873;u kho&#7843;n m&#7899;i nh&#7845;t s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#259;ng t&#7843;i tr&#7921;c ti&#7871;p t&#7841;i trang n&#224;y.</p>
